> >Has anyone here in the states purchased anything from Just Kampers in the
> >UK? I'm interested in their 3-point replacement seat belts for the back 
> >seat
> >and was wondering how the overseas shipping went.
> 
> If shipping is a hundred dollars, it may be worth it, just to get a kit.

if time is not a problem consider "surface" shipment.   it might be as low
as 10% of air freight, but consider several weeks for shipment is about
right.   ship to Japan air is 50cents the half ounce.  surface is about $2
lb, varies by item.

Bob

